alerts.title: Wind Advisory
alerts.description: ...WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 8 PM EST THIS EVENING... * WHAT...West winds 20 to 30 mph with gusts to around 45 mph. * WHERE...Portions of northeast New Jersey, southern Connecticut and southeast New York. * WHEN...Until 8 PM EST this evening. * IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects. Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may result.
